title: Guns 'N' Roses - Live In Paris,Hdrome de Vincennes (2-CD)1992
description:
Guns 'N' Roses - Live In Paris,Hippodrome de Vincennes (2-CD)1992 ak320 

Have been hearing about this show since I started file sharing and it lives up to the hype. It is one of the best sounding Gn'R shows that's NOT around. 
Well we shall fix that last part. Its now around 
Recorded Live at Hippodrome de Vincennes, Paris, France - June 06, 1992. 
Excellent Soundboard Recording -> Bootleg Silver CD :: CBR 320 kbps. 


Disc 1 
01. Its So Easy 
02. Mr. Brownstone 
03. Live & Let Die 
04. Attitude 
05. Bad Obsession 
06. Aways On The Run (With Lenny Kravitz) 
07. Double Talkin' Jive 
08. Civil War 
09. Wild Horses 
10. Patience 
11. You Could Be Mine 
12. November Rain 

Disc 2

02. Sweet Child O' Mine 
03. Welcome To The Jungle 
04. Knockin' On Heavens Door 
05. Mama Kin (With Steven Tyler & Joe Perry) 
06. Train Kept A Rollin' (With Steven Tyler & Joe Perry) 
07. Don't Cry 
08. Paradise City 

** Use Your Illusion Tour ** 

Personnel: Axl Rose, lead vocals, piano :: Slash, lead guitar, rhythm guitar, backing vocals. :: Gilby Clarke, rhythm guitar, backing vocals. :: Duff McKagan – bass, backing vocals :: Matt Sorum – drums, percussion, backing vocals. 

Guest Musicians: Lenny Kravitz; Steven Tyler and Joe Perry
